Field Detail

ENABLE_METHOD_OVERRIDE

public static final boolean ENABLE_METHOD_OVERRIDE
If this system property is set to true, the GData HTTP client library will use POST to send data to the associated GData service and will specify the actual method using the method override HTTP header. This can be used as a workaround for HTTP proxies or gateways that do not handle PUT, PATCH, or DELETE HTTP methods properly. If the system property is false, the regular verbs will be used.
